graph TD
    A[Start Epoch] --> B[Forward Pass: autocast float16]
    B --> C[Loss Calculation]
    C --> D[scaler.scale backpropagation]
    
    subgraph Optimization Mechanics
    D --> E[scaler.unscale_]
    E --> F[clip_grad_norm_ max_norm=1.0]
    F --> G[scaler.step optimizer]
    G --> H[scaler.update]
    end
    
    H --> I{Validation Loss Improved?}
    I -->|Yes| J[Save Best Checkpoint]
    I -->|No| K[Increment Patience Counter]
    K --> L{Counter > Max Patience?}
    L -->|Yes| M[Early Stopping Triggered]
    L -->|No| A
    J --> A
